\begin{itemize}
\item Amplifier gain plot. Submit a single figure with a plot showing the output vs. input data and the linear regression line from both amplifier circuits. Sample plot is shown in Figure \ref{fig:samplePlot}. Specifically, the single plot should include:
\begin{itemize}
\item Output vs. Input data from the LM358 op-amp circuit, including saturation (top Plot). Use markers.
\item Linear regression line from the linear portion of the output vs. input data from the LM358 circuit.
\item Output vs. Input data from the AD622 instrumentation amplifier circuit, including saturation. Use markers (bottom plot).
\item Linear regression line from the linear portion of the output vs. input data from the AD622 instrumentation amplifier circuit. This plot should also show output saturation when the circuit output nears the supply voltage limits. Make sure to properly annotate the plot.
\item Sample Matlab code for plotting is shown in the appendix \ref{app:postLab}
\end{itemize}
\item Answer all question in the post-lab assessment on Canvas.
\end{itemize}
